{"tid":1099435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大灣區美食]佛山環保豬屎可供食用]","createTime":"2019-04-09T19:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T06:22:16.000Z","uid":202340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23ac32b24ed907fe97c2639d0553412ad09bce93","tid":1099435,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T19:23:53.000Z","msg":"佛山市高明區一個環保豬場，聲稱用一種特殊水餵豬喝，令牠們排出的糞便「無臭味、無污染」，乾淨得能給人吃。豬場技術人員前日更即場示範將「豬屎」食落肚。 <br />\n姓張的技術員表示，一般豬隻只要喝下這種特別調製的水後，體內會產生大量益菌，不但能增加豬的抗病力，又能分解氨氮和含磷有機物質，令豬排出來糞便全無污染。經加工製造出來的有機肥料，含有多種對人體有益的多糖體、氨基酸等要素，不但可以拿來吃，還可用來泡茶喝。 <br />\n《廣州日報》  <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.wearn.com/userfile/wearn.com-life-112-8886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wearn.com%2Fuserfile%2Fwearn.com-life-112-8886.jpg&h=439c66d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20031023/3616865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20031023%2F3616865&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=3e6c4c62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20031023%2F3616865&h=f683cf9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20031023/3616865</a>"},{"pid":"b3030f5d5c17dfcbb058b7d44c96724d7affffdb","tid":1099435,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"我之前咪貼過呢則16年前舊聞。"},{"pid":"3673aff8abb912c61bea8a2de0475150bd67ce70","tid":1099435,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3030f5d5c17dfcbb058b7d44c96724d7affffdb","tid":1099435,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"我之前咪貼過呢則16年前舊聞。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T20:30:57.000Z","msg":"? binc"},{"pid":"ab54033950aa02195fa43c6d48bda1c19738e715","tid":1099435,"uid":202340,"like"